    'pctCloneTown_y': 'pctCloneTown',
    'vulnerabilityIndex_y': 'vulnerabilityIndex',
    'onlineExposure_y': 'onlineExposure',
    'eResilience_y': 'eResilience',
    'Driving_AvgIMD_y': 'Driving_AvgIMD',
    'Walking_AvgIMD_y': 'Walking_AvgIMD'
